These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: satire, scientific
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, ship
1. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | satire  | scientific |
| Transport     | ship | quad-bike  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: carrot, apple
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: tennis, badminton
1. the person eating apple is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Food    | carrot      | apple         |
| Sport   | tennis | badminton |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, coffee
There 2 different types of food: nectarine, broccoli
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Beverage   | coffee | mirinda   |
| Food       | broccoli  | nectarine |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-4::.
